import {Button, Container, Nav, Navbar, NavLink} from "react-bootstrap";
import {Link} from "react-router-dom";
import React from "react";

var style = {
    backgroundColor: "#F8F8F8",
    borderTop: "1px solid #E7E7E7",
    textAlign: "center",
    padding: "20px",
    position: "fixed",
    left: "0",
    bottom: "0",
    height: "60px",
    width: "100%",
}

var phantom = {
    display: 'block',
    padding: '20px',
    height: '60px',
    width: '100%',
}

function Footer() {
    return (
        <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg" style={phantom}>
            <Container style={style}>
                <Navbar.Brand href="#home">a_toxic</Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                    {
                        user.isAuth?
                            <Nav className="ml-auto">
                                <Nav.Link href="#home">Главная</Nav.Link>
                                <Nav.Link href="#link">Модерация контента</Nav.Link>
                                <Nav.Link href="#link2">Статистика</Nav.Link>
                                <Nav.Link href="#link3">Выйти</Nav.Link>
                            </Nav>
                            :
                            <Nav className="ml-auto">
                                <Nav.Link href="#link2">Войти</Nav.Link>
                                <Button onClick={()=>user.setIsAuth(true)}>Вход</Button>
                            </Nav>
                    }

                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Container>

        </Navbar>
       
    )
}

export default Footer;
